        h2 About the Greenhouse
        p For my SYS 2502 class this past semester, Introduction to Electromechanical Systems, my project was to design a system that could maintain a set temperature, and have all the data collection (and setpoint functionality) all controllable via the internet. The system was also designed to simulate future expected behavior to determine whether or not the greenhouse is not functioning properly or has been tampered with. I have no picture of any of the projects components, so the picture at left is just of an ordinary, pleasant-looking greenhouse (though it is the same exact greenhouse, made by IKEA). The project involved Arduino, PHP, MySQL, and Javascript (including HighCharts).
